text: L Seng Zi (; also spelt L Saing Zi or L Sai Zi) is a Burmese singer of Kachin descent. Her aunt L Khun Yi, and her cousin L Lun Wa, are also popular singers. ==Discography== *Incomparable Gratitudes (အနှိုင်းမဲ့ကျေးဇူးတော်) (2017) *Obsessed (အစွဲအလန်းကြီးသူ) (2017) *Wai Khwal Ma Ya Par Lar (2017) *Moe Kaung Kin Kha Yee (2019) ==References== ==External links== * Category:Burmese female singers Category:Living people Category:Burmese people of Kachin descent Category:Burmese pop singers Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
